Package: r8152-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: make, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Realtek r8152 USB Ethernet driver in DKMS format
 This package provides the Realtek r8152 out-of-tree USB Ethernet driver
 source for DKMS. DKMS rebuilds the module when compatible kernels are
 installed or upgraded.
